  "detailed_description": "Astrodle is an <strong><u>incremental space shooter</u></strong> that is all about collecting the essences of the Zodiac in a quest to become an immortal space god. <strong><u>Shoot</u></strong>, <strong><u>collect</u></strong>, <strong><u>upgrade</u></strong>, repeat, become a god. Sounds easy enough, right?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shoot and Collect Essences</h2>Your spaceship comes equipped with lasers and that’s too bad for the <strong><u>Blobs</u></strong>. Destroy as many as you can to collect <strong><u>Essences</u></strong> and make progress on your quest.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/7c5d3368b5e660bb1df7c1128455d461.poster.avif?t=1718804789\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/7c5d3368b5e660bb1df7c1128455d461.webm?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/7c5d3368b5e660bb1df7c1128455d461.mp4?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your Ship</h2>Your lasers are awesome but you can make them better. Spend your essences on <strong><u>Upgrades</u></strong> and take your fire power to the next level.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/64f5535fe26af869cbc8d60d17bc4497.poster.avif?t=1718804789\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/64f5535fe26af869cbc8d60d17bc4497.webm?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/64f5535fe26af869cbc8d60d17bc4497.mp4?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Revel in the Numbers</h2>Now it’s time to take a step back and <strong><u>admire the chaos</u></strong> you have unleashed on the blobs. All these numbers everywhere, isn’t that perfect?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/ae2e3abc3a5517a217cf1d7d23166578.poster.avif?t=1718804789\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/ae2e3abc3a5517a217cf1d7d23166578.webm?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/ae2e3abc3a5517a217cf1d7d23166578.mp4?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete the story</h2>Space is vast but you are not alone. <strong><u>Sagittarius</u></strong>, <strong><u>Aquarius</u></strong> and <strong><u>Taurus</u></strong> are here to guide you through your quest to become a god. It's been a very long time since they have encountered a human but that's not a problem… right?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/420bab13c64878492f393711ea2bad92.poster.avif?t=1718804789\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/420bab13c64878492f393711ea2bad92.webm?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/420bab13c64878492f393711ea2bad92.mp4?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beat the game</h2>Don't you hate when you can't tell if you have finished an idle game or not? Both game modes of Astrodle have an end that can be reached in just a day when played actively. Ideal for playing lazily <strong><u>over the weekend</u></strong>.",
  "about_the_game": "Astrodle is an <strong><u>incremental space shooter</u></strong> that is all about collecting the essences of the Zodiac in a quest to become an immortal space god. <strong><u>Shoot</u></strong>, <strong><u>collect</u></strong>, <strong><u>upgrade</u></strong>, repeat, become a god. Sounds easy enough, right?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shoot and Collect Essences</h2>Your spaceship comes equipped with lasers and that’s too bad for the <strong><u>Blobs</u></strong>. Destroy as many as you can to collect <strong><u>Essences</u></strong> and make progress on your quest.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/7c5d3368b5e660bb1df7c1128455d461.poster.avif?t=1718804789\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/7c5d3368b5e660bb1df7c1128455d461.webm?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/7c5d3368b5e660bb1df7c1128455d461.mp4?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your Ship</h2>Your lasers are awesome but you can make them better. Spend your essences on <strong><u>Upgrades</u></strong> and take your fire power to the next level.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/64f5535fe26af869cbc8d60d17bc4497.poster.avif?t=1718804789\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/64f5535fe26af869cbc8d60d17bc4497.webm?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/64f5535fe26af869cbc8d60d17bc4497.mp4?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Revel in the Numbers</h2>Now it’s time to take a step back and <strong><u>admire the chaos</u></strong> you have unleashed on the blobs. All these numbers everywhere, isn’t that perfect?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/ae2e3abc3a5517a217cf1d7d23166578.poster.avif?t=1718804789\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/ae2e3abc3a5517a217cf1d7d23166578.webm?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/ae2e3abc3a5517a217cf1d7d23166578.mp4?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete the story</h2>Space is vast but you are not alone. <strong><u>Sagittarius</u></strong>, <strong><u>Aquarius</u></strong> and <strong><u>Taurus</u></strong> are here to guide you through your quest to become a god. It's been a very long time since they have encountered a human but that's not a problem… right?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/420bab13c64878492f393711ea2bad92.poster.avif?t=1718804789\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/420bab13c64878492f393711ea2bad92.webm?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853130/extras/420bab13c64878492f393711ea2bad92.mp4?t=1718804789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beat the game</h2>Don't you hate when you can't tell if you have finished an idle game or not? Both game modes of Astrodle have an end that can be reached in just a day when played actively. Ideal for playing lazily <strong><u>over the weekend</u></strong>.",
